 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lruihao/auto-changelog-plus/refs/heads/main./README.md" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;中文&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt; | English&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A command line tool to generate changelogs from git commit history automatically.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Based on &lt;a href="https://github.com/CookPete/auto-changelog" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;auto-changelog&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="https://www.conventionalcommits.org/en/v1.0.0/" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;Conventional Commits&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt; specification.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/auto-changelog-plus" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" src='https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/images/remote/auto-changelog-plus_7979101328369740159.svg' alt="npm version"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="-installation"&gt;&lt;span&gt;📦 Installation&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#-installation" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;npm install -g auto-changelog-plus&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="-usage"&gt;&lt;span&gt;🚀 Usage&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#-usage" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Run &lt;code&gt;auto-changelog-plus&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;acp&lt;/code&gt; in the root directory of your git repository. The tool will run &lt;code&gt;git log&lt;/code&gt; behind the scenes to parse the commit history.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>⚙️ Versioning, change-log and release tool. (Superseded by https://github.com/Lruihao/auto-changelog-plus)</title><link>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/projects/hugo-fixit/fixit-releaser/</link><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 18:10:59 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/projects/hugo-fixit/fixit-releaser/</guid><category domain="https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/categories/github/">GitHub</category><description>&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="fixit-releaser" data-decreased&gt;&lt;span&gt;FixIt Releaser&lt;/span&gt;
